title: welp, another game of lucian picked and getting fed
body: This is getting old, and last game, i even fed my own lucians lane, double buffs to enemy adc at level 3, and my ally lucian still manages to go 4 and 0 in lane with no help, even one time my ally support said "i didn't do any thing" as lucian just 1v2s enemy bot lane. Sick and tired of seeing lucian's every game and getting fed, and winning.
